287
00:18:20,830 --> 00:18:22,640
I suppose I'll reluctantly

288
00:18:23,020 --> 00:18:24,220
help you.

289
00:18:40,320 --> 00:18:44,130
[Sun's Mansion]

290
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:14,510
Pingkang!

291
00:19:18,960 --> 00:19:20,510
