423
00:25:03,170 --> 00:25:03,930
Well...

424
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,290
They won't mock you.

425
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:06,350
Can they do this?

426
00:25:06,490 --> 00:25:06,900
You...

