465
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,110
Please come in.

466
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:13,270
One hundred pieces?

467
00:27:14,430 --> 00:27:15,360
Is there a problem?

468
00:27:15,750 --> 00:27:16,900
No problem, no problem.

469
00:27:17,930 --> 00:27:18,740
It's just that...

470
00:27:19,110 --> 00:27:21,900
