503
00:28:22,880 --> 00:28:25,830
-One hundred pieces!
-One hundred pieces!

504
00:28:25,850 --> 00:28:26,270
Alright.

505
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,030
Let's stop giving out leaflets.

506
00:28:28,030 --> 00:28:29,200
Come on! Follow me to the back garden.

507
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,240
