540
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:44,550
Haste makes waste.

541
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:45,720
You don't understand.

542
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:46,830
That makes sense.

543
00:29:48,840 --> 00:29:49,840
You understand.

544
00:29:50,750 --> 00:29:52,270
